headline: Regency Centers Announces Tax Information for Regency Centers 2025 Distributions
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Jan. 22, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Regency Centers Corporation (“Regency Centers” or the “Company”) (Nasdaq:REG) today announced the federal income tax treatment of its 2025 distributions to holders of its Common and Preferred stock.
